\c 70
\s1 Mazmur yang ditulis Daud untuk kondektur;
\s1 ditulis untuk menarik perhatian ALLAH.
\q1
\v 1 Ya ALLAH, berkehendaklah menolong aku!
\q2 TUHAN, cepatlah dan tolonglah aku!
\q1
\v 2 Biarlah mereka yang ingin mengambil nyawaku
\q2 merasa malu dan hina!
\q1 Biarlah mereka yang ingin menyakitiku
\q2 berbalik dan merasa malu!
\q1
\v 3 Biarlah mereka yang berkata, “Syukur! Syukur!”
\q2 mundur dan dipermalukan!
\q1
\v 4 But I hope/desire that all those who go to \add worship\add* you will be very joyful [DOU].
\q2 I hope/desire that those who love you because you saved them will shout repeatedly [HYP],
\q1 “God is great!”
\b
\q1
\v 5 As for me, I am poor and needy [DOU];
\q2 so God, come quickly to help me!
\q1 Yahweh, you are the one who saves and helps me,
\q2 so please come quickly!